sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Nuclei were isolated from cryosectioned tissues according to the following protocol: dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.ufketkw with the exception that 4',6-diamidino-2-phenylindole (DAPI) was excluded from the nuclear extraction buffer and only used to stain a subset of nuclei used for counting, SNARE-Seq2, as outlined (Nature Protocols, DOI:10.1038/s41596-021-00507-3), was performed according to the following protocol: dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.be5gjg3w, Dual RNA-Seq and ATAC-Seq
sample_data_processing: Basecalls were performed using NovaSeq Control Software v1.6.0, SNARE-Seq2 data was processed using the snarePip pipeline (github.com/huqiwen0313/snarePip), For RNA processing, AC contaminating reads were removed using cutadapt (version 3.1), For RNA processing, cell barcodes were extracted using dropEst (version 0.8.6), For RNA processing, STAR (v2.5.2b) was used to align tagged reads to the genome (GRCh38), For AC processing, snaptools (version v1.2.3) and minimap (version 2-2.20) were used fo ...
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Seurat object in R Data format, tabulated ATAC-seq captured fragments for each cell in BED-like format, raw RNA counts provided in RDS format, peak counts provided in RDS format, sample metadata table in txt format, and metadata field descriptions in txt format

sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Single cells were isolated from frozen tissues according to the following protocol: dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.7dthi6n, 10X single cell RNA sequencing was performed according to dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.7dthi6n using the 10X Chromium Single-Cell 3 Reagent Kit v3
sample_data_processing: Basecalls were performed using NovaSeq Control Software v1.7.0, Sample demultiplexing, barcode processing, and gene expression quantifications were performed with the 10X Cell Ranger v3 pipeline using the GRCh38 (hg38) reference genome, A cutoff of < 50% mitochondrial reads per cell was applied, Ambient mRNA contamination was corrected using SoupX (v1.5.0), Cell barcodes having greater than 500 and less than 5000 genes detected were kept for downstream analyses
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Seurat object in h5Seurat format, raw RNA counts provided in RDS format, sample metadata table in txt format, and metadata field descriptions in txt format
